ike":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:35:20.000Z","msg":"SPCA熟手技工"},{"pid":"39c441fddd1aa7377324b7451bfb1f59994d1b41","tid":1513123,"uid":255802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:52:09.000Z","msg":"有幼貓營養粉 有冇需要？"},{"pid":"2909574a26d662b0c9b59b7ed0ed96590dddc185","tid":1513123,"uid":212410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:15:12.000Z","msg":"唔該大家先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我試下先聯絡spca<br />\n至於領養問題我都決定唔到 一嚟我無養開貓做唔到暫養交收 二嚟好多都係成貓慣咗流浪收養好似唔太好 幼貓嘅話等我同啲動物團體聯絡咗如果有update再同大家講 謝謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ea849f115d1e7957a80b4613913e59a398c522","tid":1513123,"uid":212410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:18:28.000Z","msg":"最後一樣 831見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c577b3f99638bbd2fb504655563f41a5711dde29","tid":1513123,"uid":55425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2909574a26d662b0c9b59b7ed0ed96590dddc185","tid":1513123,"uid":212410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:15:12.000Z","msg":"唔該大家先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我試下先聯絡spca<br />\n至於領養問題我都決定唔到 一嚟我無養開貓做唔到暫養交收 二嚟好多都係成貓慣咗流浪收養好似唔太好 幼貓嘅話等我同啲動物團體聯絡咗如果有update再同大家講 謝謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:34:49.000Z","msg":"搵spca絕育放回好啦<br />\n千奇咪叫佢地幫手出領養<br />\n佢地會「評估」完覺得無辦法俾人養就直接安樂死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會安樂死條件：有丁屎咁多攻擊性、太驚人、成貓（部分）、唔靚、有病、出完領養一直都無人要"},{"pid":"9912dd46d77e1276ccbe6deb78398363046a5f26","tid":1513123,"uid":105821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:51:15.000Z","msg":"樓主住邊頭？<br />\n想去執隻幼貓返黎養<br />\n冇經驗但貓網有哂 <br />\n之前家訪咗幾次都話俾咗其他人<br />\n所以想執隻返歸<img src=\"/ass